sp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li class=\"alt\" style=\"color:inherit;background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">apt-get&nbsp;update&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">apt-get&nbsp;upgrade&nbsp;–show-upgraded&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n</ol>\r\n</pre>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#F8F8F8;text-indent:28px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;\">\r\n	配置安全属性\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#F8F8F8;text-indent:28px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;\">\r\n	增加一个系统管理员\r\n</p>\r\n<pre>\r\n<ol class=\"dp-xml\" style=\"margin-left:55px;color:#5C5C5C;background-color:#F7F7F7;\">\r\n	\r\n	<li class=\"alt\" style=\"color:inherit;background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">adduser&nbsp;example_user&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">usermod&nbsp;-a&nbsp;-G&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;example_user&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li class=\"alt\" style=\"color:inherit;background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">logout&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:black;background-color:inherit;\">ssh&nbsp;example_user@123.456.78.90&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n</ol>\r\n</pre>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#F8F8F8;text-indent:28px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;\">\r\n	现在开始，你可以用新用户加sudo来执行管理员命令了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#F8F8F8;text-indent:28px;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;\">\r\n	反激活root的SSH登录\r\n</p>\r\n<pre>\r\n<ol class=\"dp-xml\" style=\"margin-left:55px;color:#5C5C5C;background-color:#F7F7F7