om:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">u<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：预防以外删除。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">lsattr</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-a&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　显示所有文件和目录，包括以</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&quot;.&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">为名称开头字符的额外内建，现行目录</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&quot;.&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">与上层目录</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&quot;..&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-d&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　显示，目录名称，而非其内容。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-l&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　此参数目前没有任何作用。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-R&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　递归处理，将指定目录下的所有文件及子目录一并处理。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-v&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　显示文件或目录版本。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-V&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　显示版本信息。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">强制位和冒险位</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">SUID&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">SGID&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">SBIT<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">Sticky&nbsp;bit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">5.6<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件查找</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">which&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">根据</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">PATH</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">找执行文件</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">whereis&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">寻找或定位文件根据数据库文件（</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">/var/lib/mlocate</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">locale&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">updatedb</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">find&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">5.7<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">链接文件&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">ln</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">ln&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-b<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--backup&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　删除，覆盖目标文件之前的备份。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-d<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">-F</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--directory&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　建立目录的硬连接。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-f<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--force&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　强行建立文件或目录的连接，不论文件或目录是否存在。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-i<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--interactive&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　覆盖既有文件之前先询问用户。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--no-dereference&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　把符号连接的目的目录视为一般文件。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">-s<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">--symbolic&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　对源文件建立符号连接，而非硬连接。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n',NULL);
INSERT INTO `course_txt` (`id`,`content_id`,`txt`,`txt_pics`) VALUES 
 (25,25,'<div style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font: normal normal normal 12px/1.5 \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; \">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \"><strong>6.1、硬盘与Linux文件系统</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">硬盘组成</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">(盘片、马达、机械手、磁头、扇区、柱面）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">硬盘分区</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">ext2文件系统</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \"><strong>6.2、磁盘分区</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">df 磁盘信息</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-a或--all&nbsp;&nbsp; 包含全部的文件系统。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-h以可读性较高的方式来显示信息。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-i或--inodes&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示inode的信息。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-k或--kilobytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 指定区块大小为1024字节。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-l或--local&nbsp;&nbsp; 仅显示本地端的文件系统。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-T或--print-type&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示文件系统的类型。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">du 显示目录或文件的大小</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-a或-all&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示目录中个别文件的大小</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-h以K，M，G为单位，提高信息的可读性</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-s或--summarize&nbsp;&nbsp; 仅显示总计</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-S 显示个别目录的大小时，并不含其子目录的大小</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-k或--kilobytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 以1024 bytes为单位</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-m或--megabytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 以1MB为单位</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \"><br />\r\nfdisk<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 命令行工具，各种版本和环境都能用</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \"><strong>6.3、分区格式化</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">mkfs -t ext3 /dev/sda6<br />\r\nmkfs&nbsp;<br />\r\n-t vfat /dev/sda5<br />\r\nmkfs.ext3 /dev/sda6</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \"><strong>6.4、检验</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">fsck [-t&nbsp; 文件系统] [ACay] 设备名</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">-t : 给定档案系统的型式，若在 /etc/fstab 中已有定义或 kernel 本身已支援的则不需加上此参数 　　　</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; 