 (37,37,'<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	虽然html简单，但对一些新人来讲还有必要做个系统的学习，所以这一节系统地讲解一下html的一些知识和技术，希望新人能快速 入门，\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	超文本标记语言，即HTML（Hypertext Markup Language），是用于描述网页文档的一种标记语言。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		给网页提供数据\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		格式化网页\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;line-height:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;html&gt;</span> \r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&lt;head&gt;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&lt;title&gt;页面的标题&lt;/title&gt;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&lt;/head&gt;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&lt;body&gt;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	这里是网页的内容\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-family:\'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&lt;/body&gt;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-fami